<item>
            <title>[LU-13572] LNet Health should only attempt recovery of remote NIs for which it has successfully communicated with</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13572</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Recovery should be strictly for NIDs which we have already communicated with before. i.e. recovery should only trigger when we&apos;re going from a known good state, to a known bad state.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
